collection.name: Trillionaire Thugs
collection.description:
Trillionaire Thugs is a collection of 7,777 NFTs, with more than 350 Traits in 3D each representing a Thug in the hype of the hip hop universe.
Owning a Trillionaire Thug NFT grants the owner access to an exclusive community where networking and genuine connection is our priority.

Trillionaire Thugs will also be a Play to Earn game currently in development, that will be released at the end of 2022.
https://www.trillionairethugs.com/
